%93ng-ni%C3%AAn/poem-quQOXY0QlcRV1_OOENOs8A">Thù Khang Châu Vi thị ngự đồng niên - 酬康洲韋侍御同年</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%A9a-H%E1%BB%93n/author-67u8r1Npo8IzUDBZnVHSFA">Hứa Hồn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-l%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-QW1beqUlDEprAGodU0h2sA">Tuyệt cú lục thủ kỳ 3 - 絕句六首其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/T%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-trung-huy%E1%BB%81n/poem-FaLSS1kNE789Qwbtzl6yLw">Tương trung huyền - 湘中弦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-CZQp1s97hpqFaUs-3UnvYA">Cao Khải</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-VI/poem-dn_VSLLmpIobmHLctrnmqQ">Vô đề (VI) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/author-bg2Iw4F0Q1WB-Vf8_0Kqcw">Khả Mân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
